    "description_long": "This is a compact, low-profile convertible car with a deep red body and a black soft top roof. The car features angular, geometric lines and a pronounced rear spoiler, giving it a sporty appearance. The wheels are dark gray with a multi-spoke design, and the side mirrors are small and streamlined. The front end has a rectangular grille flanked by dual headlights, while the rear displays round taillights and a wide bumper. The windows are tinted light blue, and the door handles are subtly integrated into the body. The overall design suggests a modern, performance-oriented vehicle suitable for urban driving.",
